==Xerna's stolen diadem==
===Inpecting the empty display===
* {{tcond|If the player does not meet the quest requirements:}}
** '''Player:''' A high price? That'll be nice for whoever can figure it out...
** {{tbox|You do not meet all of the requirements to start the Ethically Acquired Antiquities quest.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player meets the quest requirements:}}
** '''Player:''' A high price? I guess I am somewhat of an expert on finding things for museums...
** {{tselect|Start the Ethically Acquired Antiquities quest?}}
** {{topt|Yes.}}
*** '''Player:''' Maybe I should talk to the curator to find out some more.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No.}}
*** '''Player:''' But this will have to be a job for another time.
*** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Curator Herminius===
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Curator Herminius:''' Nilsal to you, iknami. Welcome to the Grand Museum. I hope your visit is a pleasant one. If you have any questions about Varlamore, I'm happy to help.
* {{tselect|Select an option}}
* {{topt|quest=no|Could you tell me more about the early history of Varlamore?}}
* {{topt|quest=no|Could you tell me more about religion in Varlamore?}}
* {{topt|quest=no|Could you tell me more about Varlamore's recent history?}}
* {{topt|Could you tell me more about that empty display?}}
** '''Player:''' Could you tell me more about that empty display?
** '''Curator Herminius:''' Oh yes, Xerna's Diadem... Quite a shame, isn't it? Do you know anything about it?
** '''Player:''' I'm afraid not, but maybe I can help find it? I have managed to return stolen property to museums in the past.
** '''Curator Herminius:''' That would certainly be most appreciated. The local guards said they'd investigate for us, but it's not proven to be a fast process so far.
** '''Curator Herminius:''' I was starting to consider trying to find it myself, but I'm no detective. It doesn't seem to me like anything else is even out of place...
** '''Curator Herminius:''' Perhaps you'll have better luck though. Maybe you could have a look around for any sort of clues and see if you can find anything wrong.
** '''Player:''' I'll do that. Hopefully I can find something!
** '''Curator Herminius:''' Thank you, iknami.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|quest=no|Thanks. If I have any questions, I'll be sure to ask.}}

