===Talking to Curator Haig Halen after finding the diadem===
* '''Curator Haig Halen:''' Welcome to the museum of Varrock.
* {{tselect|Select an option}}
* {{topt|quest=no|Talk about Fossil Island.}}
* {{topt|I found Xerna's Diadem...}}
** '''Player:''' I found Xerna's Diadem...
** '''Curator Haig Halen:''' Ah...
** {{qact|Cutscene starts, focusing on the curator.}}
** '''Curator Haig Halen:''' So you found the diadem? That's... Er... That's wonderful news!
** '''Curator Haig Halen:''' I'm sure that the Grand Museum will be thrilled to hear it.
** '''Player:''' Do you know where I found it?
** '''Curator Haig Halen:''' I... No, why would I?
** '''Player:''' Be honest with me, curator!
** '''Curator Haig Halen:''' I don't know what you're talking about!
** '''Player:''' You can't just steal artefacts and claim them as your own for the museum!
** '''Curator Haig Halen:''' Steal?! I would never! You need to get your facts straight!
